      h3 Four Petals
      p.subtext Chamber Ensemble and Electronics, 2016
      p Four Petals is based off of an electronic composition that I wrote in 2014 of the same name. The process of translating everything that can be done with electronics into an electro-acoustic real-time form is a transformative one. New electronics were developed to be played along with the chamber ensemble. 
